{"tid":1245703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄籲警方明日不派出「速龍小隊」免引發流血衝突","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:37:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c72f2cc3b68c08f432e8dde5527dcbff26384b16","tid":1245703,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"公民黨立法會議員郭家麒表示，今日已聯同工黨議員張超雄，去信行政長官辦公室主任陳國基，要求政府盡快回應市民訴求，但直到下午5時仍未收到任何回覆。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒說，已去信監警會，希望明天派員到特首辦、政總及立法會一帶，希望能減少衝突發生及監察警方有否濫權。但監警會至今仍未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄呼籲特首林鄭月娥及警務處長盧偉聰，明天減少在場警員的數量及避免派出「速龍小隊」，以免再引發流血衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464069-20190620.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464069-20190620.htm&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8DwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=d7c11a05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464069-20190620.htm&h=df741a28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464069-20190620.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5dea0878b8a7d2ea4dc7feb9d52d13867d1dba48","tid":1245703,"uid":248470,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nuHjLLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnuHjLLY.jpg&h=c77e5184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfb見到，廣傳"},{"pid":"0fe71e7bacb8529ce85005c3cfc8ea5d0c9cbb7c","tid":1245703,"uid":50124,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"睇黎如果班狗派速龍，鎮南大將軍就會派南亞勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f44a6f7c96cb06d3ec6ae7f9b6a3a3ff869b2dc","tid":1245703,"uid":136227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"如果問佢警察編號佢冇答，而身上又冇編號，可唔可以懷疑有人扮狗？作為一個良好市民，應唔應該制止佢？"},{"pid":"9c36f9e9cbc2d3f7699848e5150886381337bb12","tid":1245703,"uid